snippet.title: Bitcoin Trends - Visualization (PAST DECADE + 2018)
snippet.description:
In this video, I show you bitcoin trends and stats from the past decade including the bitcoin market price, revenue paid to miners, the total amount of bitcoins mined, etc.

If you found this video about bitcoin trends helpful please leave a like! It helps me out a lot!

Data: https://www.kaggle.com/sudalairajkumar/cryptocurrencypricehistory/data
